":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"仲諗住下星期訂Nokia 9"},{"pid":"46f83f6a648875643bd29c96779fe5bcfc85e2de","tid":1073863,"uid":100131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> nokia9 遲咗咁多出, 由835講到855推出市場, 仲用翻粒舊845...終於都出喇, 又有單咁嘅野彈出黎"},{"pid":"359d9e9a47bda1e4d395cb46f8837778dd9689e8","tid":1073863,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"........<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88896d91f5f519a8921eec37c1262f11e341ea6a","tid":1073863,"uid":4394,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"HMD係芬蘭公司黎架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893a103ccbbd8146c10c794fe00902f15c235acd","tid":1073863,"uid":165782,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"83afb70f8610cd0746a635cbec375862ffaa2c1e","tid":1073863,"uid":29620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:31:09.000Z","msg":"可以唔洗買nokia機了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"Nokia壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b1a0d3957a565509fa2302ef05d7bba75ab1e9","tid":1073863,"uid":55951,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"88896d91f5f519a8921eec37c1262f11e341ea6a","tid":1073863,"uid":4394,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"HMD係芬蘭公司黎架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"係啊<br />\n所以Finnish Data Protection Board調查緊"},{"pid":"d557c9f8b12d4e7d940662308f1df9348605b58b","tid":1073863,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"2019年重要唔用https加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d8c992279b0a4bdd3d3fad1ea8c4bbb9a3401","tid":1073863,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216df8defc250bab8f3781b3671daa03fb0fddfb","tid":1073863,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3a52b3734fd3fbf8e9a3509b319222cba23b92","tid":1073863,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"多國政府近期對電子產品的私隱問題日益重視，華為更一度被指在通訊裝置中插入間諜晶片，引起滿城風雨。如今據路透社引述挪威公共廣播公司報道， Nokia 7 Plus 手機爆出數據洩露事件。報道指有關手機將用家所在位置、 SIM 卡號碼及手機序號等資訊傳送至中國電信管理的伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指，起初有用家發現，手機經常以未加密方式，向有關伺服器傳送資料包。而取得 Nokia 品牌授權開發有關產品的 HMD 表示，部分 Nokia 7 Plus 手機因為軟件錯誤，一度向國外伺服器傳送數據，但有關問題已被修復，而且未有透露有關國外伺服器屬於哪個國家。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭數據監管部門已於本月 21 日表示將會展開調查。雖然 HMD 否認有關指控，但如果被證明問題屬實， HMD 很可能會面臨監管當局的鉅額罰款。此外，相信新手機 Nokia 9 PureView 亦有機會被消息影響，使不少用家打消購買意欲。<br />\n<br />\n資訊安全專家  Dirk Wetter 表示，暗中傳送資訊的幕後黑手有機會是一個名為  com.qualcomm.qti.autoregistration.apk 的檔案。他指出有關軟件很可能是針對於中國發售的手機版本，但不小心安裝到當地版本的手機之中。"},{"pid":"3d23fb3a0851cf9a5bac52e70a70288b47a980a2","tid":1073863,"uid":23677,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"88896d91f5f519a8921eec37c1262f11e341ea6a","tid":1073863,"uid":4394,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"HMD係芬蘭公司黎架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"係囉 <br />\n<br />\n名創優品都係日本公司黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233df600131e6011b744e412f434bcfff7683289","tid":1073863,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}